--- Installing package ---

1. Download PKGBUILD files from https://aur.archlinux.org/
2. Verify that PKGBUILD and accompanying files are not malicious
3. Run `makepkg -si` in the directory where the files are saved

--- Upgrading packages ---

1. `git pull` in the directory with PKGBUILD files
2. `makepkg -si`

--- References ---

[1] https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Arch_User_Repository
